        <h2>Final Thought</h2>
        <p>This situation combines religious-freedom concerns, geopolitical strategy, local insecurity, and sovereignty. It’s an opportunity to lead nuanced conversations, reject simplistic narratives, and honor human dignity across faiths.</p>
